N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 8008.6 - Fees

State Regulations
(a) For records
which can be photocopied, there shall be a charge of 25 cents per page for
photocopies, not exceeding 81/2 by 14 inches in size. (b) There shall be no fee charged for: (1)
inspection of records; (2)
search for records; (3)
any certification pursuant to this
